						<textElement>
							<font fontName="SansSerif" size="7.5"/>
							<paragraph lineSpacing="Proportional" lineSpacingSize="0.9"/>
						</textElement>
						<text><![CDATA[The payment cut-off time is 5 p.m. everyday. Payments made
after 5 p.m. will be recorded as payment made on the next
business day. Their hotlines are as follows:
7-Eleven Convenience Stores: 2299 1110.
Circle K Convenience Stores: 2991 6337.
VanGO Convenience Stores : 2586 3567.
U select : 2586 3686.]]></text>
					</staticText>
