							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8.5" isBold="true"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["網上 / 電話理財"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<staticText>
						<reportElement x="0" y="10" width="259" height="60" uuid="58d235b7-a704-44b7-83ee-82955dca9181">
							<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.height" value="px"/>
						</reportElement>
						<textElement>
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<text><![CDATA[持有銀行「網上理財」或「電話理財」戶口的租戶，可以透過互聯網和
音頻電話繳交租金。你應按個別銀行系統的指示，選擇「香港房屋委員
會」作為收款商戶，並輸入你的電子繳費租戶號碼；請保留交易編號以
作記錄。請留意個別銀行的截數時間。]]></text>
					</staticText>
				</frame>
				<frame>
					<reportElement x="0" y="613" width="259" height="32" uuid="8db63231-3653-41ce-8fa8-ba63e9a205c9">
						<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.y" value="px"/>
					</reportElement>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="0" y="-1" width="259" height="12" uuid="9fe1765d-cc62-49ab-9774-94248b9862e4"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8.5" isBold="true" isUnderline="true"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["支票退回/自動轉帳被拒"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<staticText>
						<reportElement x="0" y="9" width="259" height="22" uuid="709a2550-2f42-44dc-b1f3-672a1b371bab"/>
						<textElement>
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<text><![CDATA[若閣下用以繳付租金之支票或所指定之自動轉帳因退回而未能成功繳付
租金，則有可能被徵收逾期利息。]]></text>
					</staticText>
				</frame>
				<frame>
					<reportElement x="0" y="645" width="259" height="110" uuid="0170374e-7a62-4fae-b416-62cbab70410e">
						<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.y" value="px"/>
					</reportElement>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="0" y="0" width="259" height="12" uuid="3cb1f8dc-791c-4874-92ad-84a75997e2dc"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8.5" isBold="true" isUnderline="true"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["備註："]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="0" y="10" width="14" height="11" uuid="d8712322-2cbc-4bed-a930-92f4735eb2a4"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["1)"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="14" y="10" width="245" height="21" uuid="60d64fbe-eab0-4417-bb0a-739214d7e81a"/>
						<textElement>
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["租金/暫准證費及其他費用須在每個曆月之首日上期繳付。"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="0" y="31" width="14" height="11" uuid="ad8aa39d-832e-4dcd-9a31-7cbaf3749ca2"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["2)"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="0" y="61" width="14" height="11" uuid="695849ae-faa0-445b-88d9-c3f2cb782f5a"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["3)"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="14" y="61" width="245" height="21" uuid="93256309-604c-4877-a1dc-d069e743a9da"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Top">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["請按此月結單上的付款方法繳交款項，切勿把款項交給其他人士。"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<textField>
						<reportElement x="0" y="82" width="14" height="11" uuid="ffa14588-2f41-4081-a538-9e771e246f2a"/>
						<textElement verticalAlignment="Middle">
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<textFieldExpression><![CDATA["4)"]]></textFieldExpression>
					</textField>
					<staticText>
						<reportElement x="14" y="31" width="245" height="30" uuid="201c55ab-12e2-4d28-b320-5578c2b9ae4f"/>
						<textElement>
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<text><![CDATA[不論業主有否正式催交，為免繳付租約/暫准證所訂的逾期利息，租
戶請於到期繳款日起計14天內清繳款項。]]></text>
					</staticText>
					<staticText>
						<reportElement x="14" y="82" width="245" height="28" uuid="3966ba89-87ea-4efb-80ce-2b430d84aaa4"/>
						<textElement>
							<font fontName="Arial Unicode MS" size="8"/>
						</textElement>
						<text><![CDATA[如你已繳交此月結單內的到期租金，或對此月結單有任何查詢，請聯絡所屬屋邨辦事處或商場管理公司。]]></text>
					</staticText>
				</frame>
				<frame>
					<reportElement x="0" y="765" width="259" height="31" uuid="90dc8df1-6a00-487b-a7fd-164eef22c39b">
						<property name="com.jaspersoft.studio.unit.y" value="px"/>
					</reportElement>
